### Create a new review (user only)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/reviews
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{USER_TOKEN}}

{
  "content": "Great tour!",
  "rating": 5,
  "tourId": "{{TOUR_ID}}"
}

### Get reviews by tour
GET http://localhost:5000/api/reviews/tour/{{TOUR_ID}}

### Get review by ID
GET http://localhost:5000/api/reviews/{{REVIEW_ID}}

### Update a review (user only)
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/reviews/{{REVIEW_ID}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{USER_TOKEN}}

{
  "content": "Updated review"
}

### Delete a review (user only)
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/reviews/{{REVIEW_ID}}
Authorization: Bearer {{USER_TOKEN}}